    <briefdescription>
<para>Structure <ref refid="struct_v_l53_l8_c_x___results_data" kindref="compound">VL53L8CX_ResultsData</ref> contains the ranging results of VL53L8CX. If user wants more than 1 target per zone, the results can be split into 2 sub-groups : </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Per zone results. These results are common to all targets (ambient_per_spad , nb_target_detected and nb_spads_enabled).</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Per target results : These results are different relative to the detected target (signal_per_spad, range_sigma_mm, distance_mm, reflectance, target_status). </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
